{"tid":677721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王家衛首位亞洲導演 獲授哈佛文學榮譽博士學位","createTime":"2018-05-25T12:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T09:59:26.000Z","uid":176111,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19ab4985413c3e78cc65a006c12f6a61c6fa92a2","tid":677721,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"王家衛導演於美國時間24日（星期四）上午，獲哈佛大學授予文學榮譽博士學位，以表彰他在電影藝術領域的成就及影響力，同場還有太太。同時他是首位獲頒此榮譽的亞洲導演。<br />\n<br />\n在哈佛大學官網的簡介中，王家衛被稱為「現代電影界最有影響力的導演之一」。頒授儀式上他發表感言：「能夠在擁有近400年光輝歷史的哈佛大學得此禮遇，與眾多歷史偉人諸如愛因斯坦、霍金、邱吉爾等成為校友，我感到與有榮焉。」同時他亦感謝家人及友人的支持。<br />\n<br />\n王家衛在電影上的成就，可以從他先後獲得的國際獎項上得到肯定，他先後贏過台灣金馬獎及香港電影金像獎，更憑梁朝偉、張國榮主演的《春光乍洩》獲贏得康城國影展最佳導演獎，更多次擔任康城影展、柏林影展兩大歐洲影展評<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180525/58236187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180525%2F58236187&d=S7eqwRF9ZfCTXic8CoUQf8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5e529601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180525%2F58236187&h=6e883fd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180525/58236187</a><br />\n<br />\n好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc27e83632434ffe799c2e0dd153849a571a50e3","tid":677721,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6a033362a26162a83fe48acaf10cf6f3ff48ba","tid":677721,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"衛衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc5713ce8aed85f3e528e5ed12415bc99155bd5","tid":677721,"uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea9cb01fa75ce800ed72abd9cf827c73bd62247","tid":677721,"uid":22913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"王家衛同fala 算唔算香港之光"},{"pid":"8b841342c09fbda4daf06ca20f151f5f53106522","tid":677721,"uid":53660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4c96e235e68d82cb636fcc76a9b81d40ed6d92","tid":677721,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f677eed3c2d0aee730d0663cdc0a6be08b5c64c2","tid":677721,"uid":59575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"如果有多一張船飛，你會唔會同我一齊走?"}]}